## Mandatory rules before finishing any task

1. **Run quality checks:**
   ```bash
   make quality
   ```
   Which runs:
   ```bash
   .venv/bin/ruff check src/ tests/ main.py --fix
   .venv/bin/ruff format src/ tests/ main.py
   .venv/bin/mypy src/
   .venv/bin/pytest tests/ -v
   ```

2. **If ruff errors:** fix them before finishing.
3. **If mypy errors:** fix them or document why with `# type: ignore[...]`.
4. **If tests fail:** fix code or test as appropriate.

